{"tid":1318793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜-獲委任輔警總監","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:32:31.000Z","uid":12919,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bb69b291785e216cd680d58060ab3df7c6e60257","tid":1318793,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:26:40.000Z","msg":"政府今日宣布委任楊祖賜為香港輔助警察隊總監，以接替行將退休的總監姚仰龍，任命即日生效。<br />\n<br />\n楊祖賜現年58歲，是新鴻基地產發展有限公司的市務總監，曾是香港奧運射擊代表隊隊長。<br />\n<br />\n他於1989年4月加入香港輔助警察隊為輔警警員，於2004年10月晉升為輔警警司，並於2008年12月升為輔警高級警司，隨後於2010年8月升為輔警總警司。於2013年11月1日，楊祖賜獲行政長官委任為輔警副總監。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，楊祖賜具備多方面的行動及管理經驗。於2004年，他獲頒香港輔助警察隊長期服務獎章，並於2014年獲頒第一勳扣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜　獲委任輔警總監<br />\n立場報道2016/4/15 &mdash; 14:24<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜-獲委任輔警總監/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%96%B0%E9%B4%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%B8%82%E5%8B%99%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%E6%A5%8A%E7%A5%96%E8%B3%9C-%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%BC%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%2F&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=45463067\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%96%B0%E9%B4%BB%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E5%B8%82%E5%8B%99%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%E6%A5%8A%E7%A5%96%E8%B3%9C-%E7%8D%B2%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%BC%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3%2F&h=17003615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/新鴻基地產市務總監楊祖賜-獲委任輔警總監/</a>"},{"pid":"5d5b97775be534449db6a5cb828c5a1dcb01e57e","tid":1318793,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82582fa3c7454f0273728eed7ba3faf8986af63d","tid":1318793,"uid":261852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"利益輸送?"},{"pid":"6b3b9bb1c3db45e81528046cfa732bb159544b67","tid":1318793,"ui